thread.title: BRIEF-Sekerbank FY 2017 Net Profit Decreases To 114.9 Million Lira

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Sekerbank FY 2017 Net Profit Decreases To 114.9 Million Lira
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - SEKERBANK TAS:
* FY 2017 NET PROFIT OF 114.9 MILLION LIRA VERSUS 125.2 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 NET INTEREST INCOME OF 1.26 BILLION LIRA VERSUS 1.08 BILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 NET FEE AND COMMISSION INCOME 331.1 MILLION LIRA VERSUS 287.2 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* NON-PERFORMING LOANS AT END OF 2017 1.02 BILLION LIRA VERSUS 1.08 BILLION LIRA YEAR AGO Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
